, 
<figureCitation box="[290,352,331,357]" captionStart="FIGURE 3" captionStartId="10.[151,250,1813,1837]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,181,1790]" captionTargetId="figure-23@10.[151,1436,181,1790]" captionTargetPageId="10" captionText="FIGURE 3. Chaetopleura lurida, disarticulated valves of a specimen BL 20.31; valves in dorsal view A, head valve; B, intermediate valve IV; C, tail valve. Valves in ventral view, D, head valve; E, intermediate valve IV; F, tail valve. SEM images of a specimen BL 15.9 mm length. Valves in dorsal view; G, head valve; H, intermediate valve IV, I, tail valve. J, intermediate valve IV in ventral view." pageId="5" pageNumber="456">3A–J</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation box="[364,430,331,357]" captionStart="FIGURE 4" captionStartId="11.[151,250,1817,1841]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,181,1793]" captionTargetId="figure-18@11.[151,1436,181,1793]" captionTargetPageId="11" captionText="FIGURE 4. Chaetopleura lurida, SEM images of a specimen BL 15.9 mm, A, girdle corneous hairs; B, girdle spicules; C, radular teeth. Chaetopleura hanselmani, BL 10.11 mm; valves in dorsal view, D, head valve; E, intermediate valve IV. Valves in ventral view, F, head valve; G, intermediate valve IV. SEM images of a specimen BL 10.9 mm; valves in dorsal view, H, head valve; I, intermediate valve IV; K, tail valve. J, valve IV in ventral view." pageId="5" pageNumber="456">4A–C</figureCitation>
</paragraph>
